::KitKat::

She ran up the entrance and went inside looking for Megatron.  She 
wanted to report in with him and Quickstrike.  She turned to 
Rowdy, "Ah, home sweet home at last."
She turned and saw a very large bot holding a very large gun to 
Darkmouse's head and holding another on to Twister.  She cold see 
that DarkMouse and Twister had guns aimed back at the other bot.
"OH boy, this is not the homecoming I was expecting."

She transformed into bot mode and grabbed her gun out and aimed it at 
the big bot. "I think we have a situation here. Drop your weapons 
now!"
